{"tid":570924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[叉燒撚]有冇知道呢隻叫咩部位?","createTime":"2018-02-24T07:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T18:31:53.000Z","uid":83993,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4e76d920268d5c8009cbd4cea1315d9d7246fdd2","tid":570924,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/153201_e2c6276990e3b336753e92e324efa1fc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F153201_e2c6276990e3b336753e92e324efa1fc.JPG&h=6ac59b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢隻應該係半肥瘦既一種<br />\n<br />\n但係佢白色果個位係彈牙, 唔係一舊油咁林patpat<br />\n係介乎筋同埋油之間.. 非常好食<br />\n有冇手足知道呢隻肉係豬既咩部位 買叉燒果陣應該點叫 生肉果陣係點既樣?<br />\n<br />\n常見既半肥瘦係咁既樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/12/0b/da/120bda6457de25c1bd7d7de28f91e082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F12%2F0b%2Fda%2F120bda6457de25c1bd7d7de28f91e082.jpg&h=3343c48f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a374bcde08600169ba3add14369a6a394b48ac14","tid":570924,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"梅頭？"},{"pid":"0c57434c7b49e26dd109e65003afbb8df3080ad7","tid":570924,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a374bcde08600169ba3add14369a6a394b48ac14","tid":570924,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"梅頭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"梅頭似係下面果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係兩隻都係叫梅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7080126ead48b96c9d762e4f7a9b176bf5d34af6","tid":570924,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"72b454d54ff8b74b420ee86fccd75010b24ea648","tid":570924,"uid